Invocation Name: day of the week calculator
des: Ever wonder what day you were born on? Need to know which day of the week that important meeting is? Just ask Day of the Week Calculator! Give it any date and it will give you the day of the week that date falls on past or future.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
